item.title: Middlemore Motel
item.description: Middlemore Motel A website I built for a motel in Auckland. This is the first project I built when I tried freelancing, I didn’t use a CMS as the client said he would rarely update the site’s content. I decided to just use ASP.NET, and plain HTML, CSS, and a little JavaScript
